grandma's name?


25
00:07:45.451 --> 00:07:48.286
Uh, Begoña.
Begoña Colomo.


26
00:07:49.155 --> 00:07:50.522
I remember her.

27
00:07:50.590 --> 00:07:52.190
And the Englishman.

28
00:07:52.258 --> 00:07:54.025
