115
00:44:12.636 --> 00:44:14.737
We just don't want
the little girl to be hurt.


116
00:44:19.042 --> 00:44:20.576
I'm going with you
to help you search.


117
00:44:24.248 --> 00:44:25.748
Ha ha,
it's ok, uh...


118
00:44:25.816 --> 00:44:27.517
We can take care
of it ourselves.


119
00:44:27.584 --> 00:44:28.518
We didn't mean
to bother.


120
00:44:28.585 --> 00:44:30.686
Not at all.
Really.


121
00:44:30.754 --> 00:44:33.089
Just give me a moment.

122
00:46:47.024 --> 00:46:50.860
You know? My dog
disappeared too.


123
00:46:51.862 --> 00:46:54.397
