in the Forest.


124
00:46:54.464 --> 00:46:55.998
They get disoriented.

125
00:46:56.066 --> 00:46:58.868
Don't worry. As soon
as this fog clears up,


126
00:46:58.936 --> 00:47:00.236
He'll come back
for sure.


127
00:47:00.304 --> 00:47:02.605
Sure. He's
very smart.


128
00:47:02.673 --> 00:47:05.975
Same as this one.
Isn't it true,
you damned dog?


129
00:47:06.043 --> 00:47:09.612
You know, you speak
Spanish very well.


130
00:47:09.680 --> 00:47:10.913
Almost better
than these.


131
00:47:10.981 --> 00:47:12.181
[all laugh]

132
00:47:12.249 --> 00:47:13.182
I'm learning.

133
00:47:14.418 --> 00:47:17.586
Yeah, that's what I
tell them to do: Learn.


134
00:47:25.629 --> 00:47:26.762
Well...

135
00:47:27.831 --> 00:47:29.899
It will be better
to spread out.


136
00:47:29.967 --> 00:47:34.303
Miguel, you take
Lechón and Antonio.


137
00:47:34.371 --> 00:47:35.604
I'll go
with this one.


138
00:47:35.672 --> 00:47:37.073
Why he has to
come with us?


139
00:47:37.140 --> 00:47:38.941
Because I say so.

140
00:47:39.743 --> 00:47:41.677
You follow
the River.


141
00:47:41.745 --> 00:47:44.547
Don't worry. You'll
be safe with me.


142
00:47:44.614 --> 00:47:46.916
I don't worry.

143
00:47:46.984 --> 00:47:47.984
What's the girl's name?

144
00:47:52.089 --> 00:47:53.489
Nerea.

145
00:47:53.557 --> 00:47:54.991
Her name is Nerea.

146
00:47:55.058 --> 00:47:56.125
Like her mother.

147
00:47:56.193 --> 00:47:57.927
She's our sister,
you know.


148
00:47:59.496 --> 00:48:01.998
Leave her mother
out of this.


149
00:48:03.633 --> 00:48:06.068
Let's go. We don't
have the whole day.


150
00:51:00.710 --> 00:51:02.311
Do you want one?

151
00:51:03.146 --> 00:51:04.780
Thanks.

152
00:51:04.848 --> 00:51:06.849
We don't smoke
anything else here.


153
00:51:17.093 --> 00:51:18.794
Beautiful shotgun.

154
00:51:18.862 --> 00:51:20.996
Do you hunt a lot?

155
00:51:21.064 --> 00:51:22.464
I did when
I was younger.


156
00:51:22.532 --> 00:51:25.367
I started again
recently.


157
00:51:25.435 --> 00:51:26.402
It's like riding
a bike.


158
00:51:26.469 --> 00:51:28.204
You don't forget how.

159
00:51:28.271 --> 00:51:29.772
Are you
a good shooter?


160
00:51:29.839 --> 00:51:32.775
I'm better now
than before.


161
00:51:36.646 --> 00:51:38.480
See that tree branch?

162
00:51:39.449 --> 00:51:40.716
Yeah.

163
00:51:54.164 --> 00:51:55.331
Good.
[chuckles]


164
00:52:14.584 --> 00:52:16.252
[chuckles]

165
00:53:40.804 --> 00:53:42.805
I'm going this way.

166
00:53:42.872 --> 00:53:45.674
Let's meet by that car.

167
00:54:15.638 --> 00:54:17.806
Be careful.

168
00:54:17.874 --> 00:54:18.807
What?

169
00:54:18.875 --> 00:54:20.542
You may get lost.

170
00:54:20.610 --> 00:54:23.612
We can end up
searching for you too.


171
00:54:24.647 --> 00:54:27.683
Just in case,
don't stray too far.


172
00:54:28.618 --> 00:54:30.652
It can be dangerous.

173
00:54:39.162 --> 00:54:40.429
Good morning.

174
00:54:41.064 --> 00:54:42.231
Good morning.

175
00:54:42.298 --> 00:54:43.232
