Good morning.


176
00:54:43.299 --> 00:54:45.000
Forgive us for
intruding like this.


177
00:54:45.068 --> 00:54:46.902
We've spent the whole
morning walking
around the Forest,


178
00:54:46.970 --> 00:54:50.873
And we thought
you could offer us
something to drink.


179
00:54:50.940 --> 00:54:53.208
Isabel: Sure, sure.
Take a seat, please.


180
00:54:59.115 --> 00:55:00.983
You're very kind.

181
00:55:01.050 --> 00:55:03.051
